  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/p0w3n3d">p0w3n3d</a> 9 hours ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">It keeps me thinking that every company loves &quot;those guys&quot; who create OpenSource but won&#x27;t give them a broken penny, nor support them in any other way<p>Servants! Just do your open source magic, We&#x27;re impatient! Ah and thanks for all the code, our hungry hungry LLMs were starving.</div>
